      • getSequence

        public Sequence getSequence(int offset)
                     throws DAOException
        Enables retrieving sequences in the database without loading everything memory

        Expected usage is long count = getSequenceCount(); int offset = 0; while( offset < count ) { Sequence sequence = dao.getSequence(offset); // do something with sequence }

        Returns:
        Sequence at the specified offset
        Throws:
        DAOException
